{"id":"4266","name":"bright-early-top-o-the-mornin-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Top O&#x2019; The Mornin&#x2019; Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-03-17T10:00:00-05:00","tags":["charlie tygard","discrimination","downtown presbyterian church","erik cole","gender identity","megan barry","metro arts commission","Music City","music city center","nashville convention and visitors bureau","pandora","public art","radnor lake rambo","rate hike","rocketown","ronnie steine","sxsw","tva","wine store"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/peppysis/3359844751/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3660/3359844751_8908eee02a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Good morning, Nashville, and happy St. Patrick&#x2019;s Day! &#xA0;Councilman Charlie Tygard has chosen to <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/bill-spread-public-art-across-county-deferred-indefinitely?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">hold off on a bill he was sponsoring that would have reworked our public art funding to spread the love all across the city rather than just downtown</a>. As much as we&#x2019;d love to see some more riverfront rollercoasters, naked people and giant buffaloes spring up in other parts of Nashville, it looks like the Metro Arts Commission is doing a fine job of this on their own and Councilman Tygard doesn&#x2019;t feel they need the bill anymore.</p><ul><li><strong>Measure it out</strong>. Nashvillians are making a splash this year at SXSW and <a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=15925\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">trying to prove to the world that there are no other music cities quite like this Music City</a>. Of course, you all know where we stand on this issue.</li><li><strong>Pandora&#x2019;s box.</strong> Speaking of luring people to our fair city, the Nashville Convention &amp; Visitors Bureau is <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/entertainment/22858603/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">kicking around a new concept of using Pandora internet radio to give people a little taste of the Nashville flavor</a>. For the next month or so, there will be a <a href=\"http://www.visitmusiccity.com/visitors/pandora\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.visitmusiccity.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Music City button that listeners can click to hear some of the best Nashville tunes</a> that are hopefully not all country.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces.</strong> Downtown Presbyterian <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12152006\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">might be getting a boozy new neighbor</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12153452\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Rocketown kids are getting into the parking business</a> and learning a little along the way &#x2026; This is the first we&#x2019;ve heard of the <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/mayor-dispels-rumor-about-belle-meade-gun-ban?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Radnor Lake Rambo</a> &#x2026; Council members Megan Barry, Ronnie Steine and Erik Cole are <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100317/NEWS0202/3170369/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">urging Metro to investigate private employers accused of discrimination based on gender identity</a> &#x2026; We can&#x2019;t remember if we told you about the <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/219cc541-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">TVA&#x2019;s latest rate hike scheduled for April</a> because we&#x2019;ve officially lost count of these.</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/peppysis/3359844751/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Peppysis</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/08/04/bright-early-practice-makes-perfect-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Practice Makes Perfect Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Practice Makes Perfect Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/11/25/bright-not-so-early-ars-gratia-artis-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; (Not So) Early: Ars Gratia Artis Edition\">Bright &amp; (Not So) Early: Ars Gratia Artis Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}